column5: Since the ice condition for this year is not stable, just want to ask is anyone fishing on open water for pan fish now?  Thanks in advance!
most Lake O tributaries are ice free
Lotsa panfish AND ice in the Kawarthas...
Lotsa open water in Niagara, and the fish are confused
fished the Holland river for a half hour on Thurs. No hits just wanted to try out my new noodle rod.
Tons of ice out there for pan fishing...
